            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "傳統盟友裂痕加深 調查顯示超半數加拿大人將美國視為最大安全威脅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】-- 超過半數加拿大人認為美國目前對其國家安全構成最大威脅，這鮮明地反映出這兩個傳統盟友之間裂痕的擴大程度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Nanos Research Group為彭博新聞社進行的調查顯示，55%的受訪者認為美國對加拿大安全構成的威脅最大。約15%的受訪者認為中國是最大威脅，另有14%的受訪者指出俄羅斯是最大威脅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次調查於1月31日至2月4日進行，正值美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>對格陵蘭島發出一系列威脅、公開抱怨北約並揚言準備對加拿大進一步加徵關稅之際。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1509d1aa-3fe1-35bd-ad28-0279b1209a1f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普的貿易政策及其不時流露的「加拿大應成為美國第51個州」的言論，已在加拿大引發民憤。作為加拿大長期最重要的盟友，美國如今已成為許多加拿大人避之不及之地，跨境旅行量急劇下降。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MbIGILJJ5mnf0uyyhifieQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4827ba51ec9586048aa1ba06155d4616\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">渥太華大學國際事務教授Roland Paris曾擔任前總理賈斯汀·特魯多的外交政策顧問，他表示這項調查結果凸顯了當前加拿大社會的「主流情緒」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這些數據有助於解釋為何在特朗普重掌白宮並開始鼓吹將加拿大變為第51個州的一年後，加拿大人仍持續抵制赴美旅行和美國商品，」Paris在郵件中寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「有人或許認為特朗普的言辭風格和經濟威脅是精明的談判策略，但這些結果表明它們對重要關係造成了多麼深重的損害。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Poses Greater Security Threat Than China, Canada Says in Poll</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Mario Baker Ramirez.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8B%E8%A3%82%E7%97%95%E5%8A%A0%E6%B7%B1-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%B6%85%E5%8D%8A%E6%95%B8%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-123712880.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-21 02:15:00",
